1. *Uopšte* ne znam da li ću biti tu večeras. (I don't know at all if I'll be there tonight.)
2. Ne razumem zašto je on to napravio, jer *uopšte* nisam znao da je to bila njegova želja. (I don't understand why he did it, because I didn't know at all that it was his wish.)
3. *Uopšte* ne razumem o čemu se radi. (I don't understand at all what this is about.)
4. *Uopšte* se nisam osećala dobro. (I didn't feel at all good.)
5. Ne verujem da ću biti u mogućnosti da to napravim, jer *uopšte* ne znam kako. (I don't believe I'll be able to do it, because I don't know at all how.)